title: Independent Candidate Shoaib Ameer wins PP-281 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Independent Candidate, Shoaib Ameer has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-281, Layyah-III by securing 38,353 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Muhammad Tahir of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz who bagged 34,870 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 59.89%.
